  <p class="intro-content bd-lead" i18n-message="Quickly start using ModalLayer."></p>
</div>
<hr>
<div class="content bd-content">
  <h3 id="introduction" i18n-message="introduction"></h3>
  <p i18n-message="ModalLayer is a modal window written by native JavaScript for front-end display. You can directly use or customize your own modal window."></p>
  <h3 id="download" i18n-message="download"></h3>
  <p><a href="https://github.com/snwf/ModalLayer/archive/master.zip" target="_blank" i18n-message="click to download"></a> <span i18n-message="or go to"></span> <a href="https://github.com/snwf/ModalLayer" target="_blank">Github</a></p>
  <h3 id="build" i18n-message="build"></h3>
  <div>
    <p>
      <span i18n-message="The CSS files are compressed using CleanCSS, and the final generated files are located in the"></span>
      <kbd>./dist/css</kbd>
    </p>
    <p>
      <span i18n-message="JavaScript files use Babel for ES6 compatibility processing (or not), and then use Google Closure Compiler for compilation and compression, and the final generated files are located in the"></span>
      <kbd>./dist/js</kbd>
    </p>
    <div>
      <span i18n-message="Execute the following commands in the project root directory in sequence"></span>
      <div class="highlight">
        <p>node ./build/build.js</p>
        <p class="mb-0">node ./dist/compiler.js</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p i18n-message="If an error message appears, you need to solve it and execute it again."></p>
  </div>
  <h3 id="project-structure" i18n-message="project structure"></h3>
  <div class="highlight">
    <pre>
